<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>[سورة الغاشية <span class="c2">(٨٨)</span>: الآيات ١٧ الى ٢٠]<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَفَلا يَنْظُرُونَ إِلَى الْإِبِلِ كَيْفَ خُلِقَتْ <span class="c2">(١٧)</span> وَإِلَى السَّماءِ كَيْفَ رُفِعَتْ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span> وَإِلَى الْجِبالِ كَيْفَ نُصِبَتْ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span> وَإِلَى الْأَرْضِ كَيْفَ سُطِحَتْ <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>